# Symfony deploy
mkdir -p cache/ log/
./symfony project:permissions
./symfony doctrine:build --all --and-load



# Action List

-Ability to set Date/Time to task urgency
-Ability to set condition to task importance
-Email reminders, along with reason why tasks are important (the equivalent of nagging)
-Task categories (work, personal)
-Ability to drag tasks into a weekly planner
-User registration (many users to one install)
-Use of MITs (most important things), ability to set 3 per day, and a follow up to make sure they're completed
